## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all aspects of technological changes in law firms, particularly those that are proprietary or not widely reported. Additionally, the rapid pace of technological advancement means that new developments may have emerged since the publication of the sources used. The findings are also limited to the perspectives and insights provided by the selected articles and may not reflect the full diversity of experiences across different law firms.